body_html: @tawantinsuyu, unfortunately no, we won't downgrade the default version, because that would break users who already updated. To use an older version, an easy way is to use docker. You can also find the previous .whl from our web site and install that, but we don't recommend that. Good luck. Thanks!

body: @tawantinsuyu, unfortunately no, we won't downgrade the default version, because that would break users who already updated. To use an older version, an easy way is to use docker. You can also find the previous .whl from our web site and install that, but we don't recommend that. Good luck. Thanks!
